    "benefits": "Arachnothryx stenostachya is a plant species that has been studied for its potential health benefits. Although limited information is available, some research suggests that the plant may have antioxidant and anti-inflammatory properties. These properties could potentially help to protect against cell damage and reduce inflammation in the body. However, more research is needed to fully understand the plant's health benefits and potential uses. Further studies are required to confirm the plant's efficacy and safety for human consumption.",
    "parts": "Arachnothryx stenostachya is a plant species that is native to Mexico and Central America. Unfortunately, there is limited information available on the medicinal properties and parts of Arachnothryx stenostachya. However, it is a member of the Rubiaceae family, which includes many plants with known medicinal properties. Further research is needed to determine the specific medicinal parts and uses of Arachnothryx stenostachya. Studies on this plant are essential to unlock its potential benefits.",
